{
  "chapter": 58,
  "chapter_summary": "本章讲述寇仲和徐子陵在船上得知李密颁下\"蒲山公令\"追杀他们，赏金丰厚。萧大姐、香玉山和云玉真商议应对之策，云玉真建议不时亮相以损李密声誉。寇仲与徐子陵讨论如何赚钱建立势力，计划运私盐发大财。素素对香玉山产生好感，寇仲徐子陵有所察觉。随后李子通率船队拦截，要求交出寇仲徐子陵，寇仲接受赌约准备与李子通一战。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 3,
      "line_end": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "我刚探听过敌情。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 5,
      "line_end": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "那里来了敌人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 9,
      "line_end": 9
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "对我们来说，这世上只有两种人，就是认识的和不认识的。而认识的又可细分作两类，就是朋友和敌人，凡不是朋友，可一概视作敌人。你说义气山是否我们的朋友？美人儿师傅是朋友吗？当然不会。所以在未澄清前他们都要暂被视作敌人，那探听他们的事，是否即探听敌情呢？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 11,
      "line_end": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你若不是吃错了药，就是患了失心疯。只不过偷听了别人说话，都可兴奋到语无伦次。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 21,
      "line_end": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "听到甚么？有屁快放！看是否值得斟酌。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 25,
      "line_end": 27
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "我偷听到一个女敌人的喘息声。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 29,
      "line_end": 29
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "女敌人的喘息声？是云玉真还是萧大姐？她两个都似爱喘息的那种女人。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 31,
      "line_end": 33
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "爱喘息的女人，亏你这假扮正人君子的色鬼才想得出来，令闻者不由生起行云布雨的遐想。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 35,
      "line_end": 37
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你这小子今趟是真的疯了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 39,
      "line_end": 41
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "我刚才摸了美人儿师傅。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 43,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "摸哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 45,
      "line_end": 45
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "她的纤纤玉手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 47,
      "line_end": 47
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "枉我还以为是甚么重要位置。她教我们鸟渡术时不也摸过我的手吗？早先她说任你亲嘴，你为何又落荒而逃？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 49,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "这叫此一时也，彼一时也。今次是本少爷主动，自不可一概而论。给我摸了后，她却装作若无其事的躲入房中，给我功聚双耳，立时追听到这女敌人竟倚门喘息，可知我对她的吸引力是多么厉害。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 53,
      "line_end": 57
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "去你奶奶的吸引力，这女人会是好人吗？李秀宁给你的教训还不够？现在我们是去为娘报仇……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 59,
      "line_end": 61
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "且莫动气。你见识浅本少爷不怪你。因你不知道有谈笑用兵这着兵家最高境界。坏女人有甚么不好？最少是对那些事经验丰富，可负起对初哥的指导大任。所以当日我改她的绰号作美人儿师傅，可算是有先见之明。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 63,
      "line_end": 71
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "其实我并非因她的反应而开心，而是为我们两兄弟而开心。想想当日我们遇到她时仍是多么潦倒和自卑，但现在不但可以摸她而不被责骂，还能使她觉得我是个有资格可以摸她的男人，可见我们已挣得点江湖地位。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 73,
      "line_end": 77
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你令我想起沾沾自喜的暴发户，又或不择手段去求官求财的势利小人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 79,
      "line_end": 81
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "说得最对就是'不择手段'这四字真言。若不是不择手段，就是绑手绑脚，就不够人斗。李密因懂不择手段，所以坐了瓦岗军的龙头位。当然！我的不择手段只针对敌人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 83,
      "line_end": 87
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "对不起！我对这四字真言的理解却和仲少有点出入。若要顾及朋友，就非不择手段！翟让不但是李密的上司，更是战友和恩人，那才叫不择手段。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 89,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "你发脾气主要是不满我去勾结美丽的女敌人，唉！一世人两兄弟，怎说怎好！至多是小弟改找香闺设在天香楼的另一位美人儿师傅玉玲姑娘好了。希望我今趟的先见之明比较灵验点。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 95,
      "line_end": 99
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你在故意逗我笑。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 101,
      "line_end": 101
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "这世上我寇仲甚么都不怕，最怕就是见到陵少爷发脾气不高兴。嘿！有件事我一直想问你，李大哥究竟算不算我们的兄弟？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 103,
      "line_end": 107
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "我倒没想过这问题，你为何会这样问呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 109,
      "line_end": 109
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "我们认识素姐，至少比认识李大哥早了个把时辰，所以该是与素姐亲近点。放着素姐这么好的女子，李靖都不懂爱护和照顾，我心里很不舒服。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 111,
      "line_end": 115
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_da_jie",
      "speaker_name": "萧大姐",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快到厅子来，有要事告诉你们呢！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 117,
      "line_end": 119
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_da_jie",
      "speaker_name": "萧大姐",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "刚收到最新消息，李密声称你们杀了他爱将'飞羽'郑踪，所以颁下了'蒲山公令'，誓要把你两人的头颅割下来。凡能用计将你们生擒活捉者，除赏千两黄金外，李密会用之为军师；拿头颅去领赏者，则可封作他的大将。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 125,
      "line_end": 129
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "素素",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怎办才好？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 133,
      "line_end": 133
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我才不怕他呢！我不和他算账，他已是不知多么走运，还欺到我们两兄弟头上来。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 135,
      "line_end": 137
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_yu_shan",
      "speaker_name": "香玉山",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "寇兄勿动气，李密现在声势雄盖天下，万众归心。这么公然颁下追杀令，显有不惜一切对付你们的决心。扬州事了后，小弟会安排两位大哥避避风头，切不要意气用事。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 139,
      "line_end": 145
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_da_jie",
      "speaker_name": "萧大姐",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "李密现在是最有机会成为皇帝的人，又懂收买人心，故天下豪杰，莫不以他马首是瞻。他这么重赏之下，定有很多盲从之辈来找你们麻烦，识时务者为俊杰，你们躲上一躲，绝没有人敢说你们是胆小怕事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 147,
      "line_end": 151
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "云玉真",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "李密颁下'蒲山公令'实属不智，因为一天你们仍活得好好的，他就下不了台。时间愈久，对他的声誉损害愈大。最好你们能不时在这里那里亮亮相，那他就更骑虎难下。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 153,
      "line_end": 157
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好！他想赶绝我们，我们就誓与他拚争到底，教他睡难安寝，食不知味。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 159,
      "line_end": 161
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_yu_shan",
      "speaker_name": "香玉山",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "而这件事却使两位大哥声名更盛，现在已有人将你们与跋锋寒、杨虚彦、'多情公子'候希白这几个人相提并论，认为你们是四阀的世家子弟外，最杰出的后起之秀。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 163,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_yu_shan",
      "text": "香小子是听谁说的？你曾上岸四处去偷听别人说话吗？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 167,
      "line_end": 169
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "素素",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "小仲！说话检点些好吗？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 171,
      "line_end": 171
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这小子今天太兴奋了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 173,
      "line_end": 173
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_yun_yu_zhen",
      "text": "美人儿师傅对我们那么好，做徒弟的自然特别开心。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 175,
      "line_end": 177
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_da_jie",
      "speaker_name": "萧大姐",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "趁尚有点时间才吃晚饭，不若我们商量一下怎样应付那昏君的事吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 181,
      "line_end": 183
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "候希白究竟是怎么样的人，为何会有个这么古怪的外号？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 185,
      "line_end": 187
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_yu_shan",
      "speaker_name": "香玉山",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "问云帮主就最清楚了！她与候希白曾有一面之缘。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 189,
      "line_end": 189
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "云玉真",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不想提起这个人。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 191,
      "line_end": 191
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_da_jie",
      "speaker_name": "萧大姐",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "甚么多情？只是处处留情罢了！奇怪是他欢喜勾三搭四，事实上却从没有人听过他曾和女子欢好。这人的来历，比之杨虚彦和跋锋寒更神秘。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 193,
      "line_end": 195
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_da_jie",
      "speaker_name": "萧大姐",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "可以谈正事了吗？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 197,
      "line_end": 197
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_xiao_da_jie",
      "text": "萧大姐请说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 199,
      "line_end": 199
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_da_jie",
      "speaker_name": "萧大姐",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "要令杨广相信你们，首先要投其所好，报喜不报忧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 201,
      "line_end": 203
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_yu_shan",
      "speaker_name": "香玉山",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "杨广的情绪极不稳定，不时会从睡梦中惊醒，口呼冤鬼索命。就算言笑甚欢时，也不能受半点刺激，下面的人一句话听不入他的耳，轻则杖责，重则斩首。所以人人都顺着他的语气与喜恶说话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 205,
      "line_end": 209
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "素素",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他的武功厉害吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 211,
      "line_end": 211
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "云玉真",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他的武功乃杨坚亲传，当然有两下子。不过这么多年被酒色蚕食身心，现在能剩下多少斤就很难说了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 213,
      "line_end": 217
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这昏君真难侍候。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 221,
      "line_end": 221
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "素素",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "助人助到底，待会你们记紧为香公仔疗治旧患。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 223,
      "line_end": 223
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "你怎可答应得这么爽快呢？我本想以此事拖着香小子，教他不敢胡作妄为的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 231,
      "line_end": 233
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "我只是为了素姐。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 235,
      "line_end": 235
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "难道看不出那小子是为了想我们为他治伤，才故意讨好素姐吗？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 237,
      "line_end": 239
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "若香玉山将来敢负素姐，我徐子陵头一个不会饶他。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 241,
      "line_end": 243
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "我们该怎样对付李密这狗贼呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 247,
      "line_end": 247
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "除非你手上有千军万马，否则能拿他怎样？只是王伯当这个贱种我们已奈何不了他，何况李密？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 249,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "此言深合我意，现在他是迫到我们头上来，所以我们必须建立自己的班底，再极力招兵买马，万事无财不行，我打算在起出'杨公宝库'前，先向香小子要一笔钱，有了钱自然好办事。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 253,
      "line_end": 255
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "我们是为了娘才做这件事，怎可要人家的钱？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 257,
      "line_end": 257
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "唉！为甚么近来我提出的主意，你都不同意呢？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 259,
      "line_end": 261
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "要赚钱就凭我们的一对手去赚回来。横竖有段日子我们要潜踪匿迹，索性去把我们藏在'学艺滩'那批私盐起出来，运往西北发大财，有了钱后买间大屋作为基地，那时你要闭起门称王称霸或是怎样都可以。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 263,
      "line_end": 267
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "此事宜早不宜迟，趁老爹截断了宋阀的财路，盐价大起时，我们狠很的赚他一笔，哈！今趟发达了！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 269,
      "line_end": 271
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "素素",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "是否恼了姐姐呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 275,
      "line_end": 277
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "恼姐姐甚么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 279,
      "line_end": 279
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "素素",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "恼姐姐迫你们去为香公子治病。唉！他的人品并不是你们想像那么差的。他还告诉人家少年时斗蟋蟀的事，原来蟋蟀是有灵性的呢！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 281,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "姐姐是否喜欢上他呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 287,
      "line_end": 289
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "素素",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "只是谈得来吧！姐姐都说过不嫁人嘛！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 291,
      "line_end": 293
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_yu_shan",
      "speaker_name": "香玉山",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是李子通的船，若今趟他亲自来，我们就有天大麻烦了。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 303,
      "line_end": 305
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_yu_shan",
      "text": "香公子不是在黑白两道都很吃得开吗？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 307,
      "line_end": 307
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "素素",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "小仲呀？这时候还要说这种话？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 309,
      "line_end": 309
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_yu_shan",
      "speaker_name": "香玉山",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "每逢牵涉到争天下，儿子与老子都没有人情讲，何况我们巴陵帮又与李子通一向没有来往。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 311,
      "line_end": 313
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们也听过这人，却知得不够详尽。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 315,
      "line_end": 315
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "云玉真",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "李子通是东海的黑道霸主，心狠手辣，先在长白山起义，渡淮后曾拥杜伏威为领袖，后来不知为了甚么原因与杜伏威反目，率众占据海陵，自称上将军，声势极盛。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 317,
      "line_end": 319
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_da_jie",
      "speaker_name": "萧大姐",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他的'竹节铜鞭'形如长棒，名列'奇功绝艺'之林，可软可硬，专破内家真气，非常厉害。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 321,
      "line_end": 323
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_da_jie",
      "speaker_name": "萧大姐",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两位公子和素素姑娘不若到舱内避避，让我们来应付他们好了。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 325,
      "line_end": 327
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那避得这么多，可否借把刀甚么的给我，小陵负责照顾素姐。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 329,
      "line_end": 331
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_yu_shan_de_shou_xia",
      "speaker_name": "香玉山的手下",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "徐爷要甚么兵器？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 333,
      "line_end": 333
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_xiang_yu_shan_de_shou_xia",
      "text": "我不用兵器。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 335,
      "line_end": 335
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "云玉真",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "小陵不用兵器吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 339,
      "line_end": 339
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_yun_yu_zhen",
      "text": "我的手就是兵器。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 341,
      "line_end": 341
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_yu_shan",
      "speaker_name": "香玉山",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "想不到李子通的势力扩张到这里来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 351,
      "line_end": 351
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zi_tong",
      "speaker_name": "李子通",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "请问是否二当家萧铣兄在船上主持大局呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 357,
      "line_end": 359
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_da_jie",
      "speaker_name": "萧大姐",
      "listener": "char_li_zi_tong",
      "text": "原来真是李龙头大驾亲临，萧环失敬！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 361,
      "line_end": 361
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zi_tong",
      "speaker_name": "李子通",
      "listener": "char_xiao_da_jie",
      "text": "原来是人称'骚娘子'的萧大姐，那看在令兄分上，今趟李某人就按江湖规矩办事，大家留个情面。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 365,
      "line_end": 367
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zi_tong",
      "speaker_name": "李子通",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "你两人乖乖随李某去吧！保证你们荣华富贵，享之不尽。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 381,
      "line_end": 383
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "云玉真",
      "listener": "char_li_zi_tong",
      "text": "巨鲲帮云玉真，向李将军问好，不知……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 387,
      "line_end": 389
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zi_tong",
      "speaker_name": "李子通",
      "listener": "char_yun_yu_zhen",
      "text": "原来是云帮主，竟是长得这么标致，怪不得令江湖这么多好汉子迷恋不已。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 391,
      "line_end": 393
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_yu_shan",
      "speaker_name": "香玉山",
      "listener": "char_li_zi_tong",
      "text": "晚辈香玉山，家父香贵，请问李将军因何事要带走晚辈这两位兄弟呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 395,
      "line_end": 397
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zi_tong",
      "speaker_name": "李子通",
      "listener": "char_xiang_yu_shan",
      "text": "即管尔父亲来，李某都不须向他请示吧？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 399,
      "line_end": 401
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_li_zi_tong",
      "text": "管你是李子通还是李不通，想要我们听命，就拿点真功夫出来，我两兄弟怕过甚么人来。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 403,
      "line_end": 405
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zi_tong",
      "speaker_name": "李子通",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "英雄出少年，难怪老杜亦对你两人另眼相看。不若我们订个赌约，只要本人在百招之内，破你两人联手，你们以后就乖乖的跟着我，听李某的吩咐如何。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 407,
      "line_end": 411
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_li_zi_tong",
      "text": "破不了又如何？我可不要你跟在身旁做狗呢！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 58,
      "line_start": 413,
      "line_end": 415
    }
  ],
